{
  "stem": "11133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and my father, the three of us, because we met in the last camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 13, almost 14, because my birthday was on the 28th of May.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember-- I remember that we weren't welcomed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here we thought we had survived the war, and we would be, you know, welcomed, but we weren't at all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If there was any-- you know, that's when I really felt anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were really told, you know, we shouldn't have survived, Hitler didn't do enough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You felt like you didn't want to stay there for a very long time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the 28th of May, it was my birthday, and the only thing I wanted was to go to a movie.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my mother arranged for me to go to the movie-- but I didn't have any clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were staying with some people, and I borrowed a skirt and a top from this lady.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the skirt-- I had to wind like three times around me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had weighed 65 pounds, and I was as tall as I am now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was pretty skinny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah, 35 kilos-- 70 pounds, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I had-- you know, I went to the movies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember to this day what I saw, it was Deanna Durbin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was some sort of a show called, in Polish, [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, it was some sort of a school for girls-- you know, adolescent girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was-- to me it was absolutely charming, and she had a beautiful voice, and she was singing in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But shock of shocks, I saw myself for the first time in a full-length mirror.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I couldn't believe what I saw, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
